steps.html_instructions: Take the ramp on the left onto I-10 E
Keep right at the fork to stay on I-10 E, follow signs for San Antonio
Take exit 556 A for TX-1604 Loop/Anderson Loop
Keep left at the fork, follow signs for TX-1604 Loop E/Anderson Loop
Keep right at the fork, follow signs for TX-1604 Loop E/Anderson Loop
Keep left at the fork, follow signs for TX-1604 Loop E and merge onto TX-1604 Loop E/Charles William Anderson Loop

Take the ramp on the left onto I-10 E/US-90 E
Continue to follow I-10 E
Take exit 768B on the left for Interstate 45 S toward Galveston
Take exit 47C on the left for McKinney St
